 anna smiled and her smile was reflected by him she grew thoughtful and he became serious some supernatural force drew eyes to face she was charming in her simple black dress charming were her round arms with their bracelets charming was her firm neck with its thread of pearls charming the straying curls of her loose hair charming the graceful light movements of her little feet and hands charming was that lovely face in its animation yet there was something terrible and cruel in her charm 
