 bring the light here fiodor bring the lantern here said levin examining the heifer like the dam though the color takes after the sire a perfect beauty long and broad in the haunch she a beauty now vassilii fiodorovich he addressed the bailiff quite forgiving him for the buckwheat under the influence of his delight in the heifer 
